A CCTV footage of an alleged tsotsi who had a bad day in office has surfaced on social media. In the video, a man is seen minding his own business when the suspect being perused came running towards him. But the man, who appeared to have not been part of the chase, would not let the tsosti pass freely. He reacted quickly with a two-feet that brought the tsosti to the ground. The suspect got up and tried to run again but the man gave him another two-feet. The thug was eventually cornered. The incident happened in Bethal, Mpumalanga. Many people on social media appreciated what the man did.      